# opengd77-map edits

Read [`AGENTS.md`](../AGENTS.md) first.

## Channel map (`opengd77-channel-map.html`)

- Single-page tool: inline CSS/JS is fine; Leaflet from CDN is the current pattern.
- Parse OpenGD77 CSV by **column header name**, not index.
- Zone hulls use the same coordinate filters as channel markers (`Use Location`, skip `0,0`).
- A channel may appear in multiple zones — each zone hull includes shared members independently.
- Mapbox tokens: `localStorage` only; never commit tokens or require a server.

## Scope

- No build toolchain unless explicitly requested.
- Do not add committed sample codeplugs; use gitignored `sample-exports/` for local CSVs.
